<br>
I originally believed that Feir'Dal were Wood Elves, but i was told otherwise by some that i hold in high regard. So i changed my beliefs going with the more experienced one's word. <br>
<br>
Turns out i was the correct one afterall. <br>
the Koada'Dal are the High Elves, not the Wood Elves as i have in my story. There are a few references to that in my story, but i'm too lazy to change them so i wish to clear up any confusion...from henceforth i will refer to the different Elvish races of Norrath correctly.<br>
<br>
Thanks for reading  my story thus far, soon to come, my blunderings at my Ceremony of Binding. if you weren't there to see it, you'll get an in-character and out of character view on it i hope it brings you a good laugh or two...<br>
well i bid you a good day..<br>
